<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-43-0281 </DOCNO><TEXT>In the system described, a pressure sensor and its associated electronicsare optically powered by a 20 mw laser and a photovoltaic cell via anoptical fiber. The sensor is periodically interrogated and sends themeasures obtained back to the central unit using an LED and a secondfiber. The results obtained as well as the expected evolution will bedescribed.</TEXT></DOC>